{"tid":537003,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"陳展鵬台慶fashion show明詩助興","createTime":"2018-01-22T10:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T22:56:34.000Z","uid":33370,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4924dfd42238d43ef78f3344c43e596623779ca7","tid":537003,"uid":33370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/22/180310_a9c3af78fcb0bb87b7125cc6a7cea4cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F180310_a9c3af78fcb0bb87b7125cc6a7cea4cf.png&h=176bbb33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/22/180242_4cb96804f8d6acf0c0a181607842b242.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F180242_4cb96804f8d6acf0c0a181607842b242.png&h=65747040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無綫嘅萬千星輝頒獎禮將於今晚喺電視城舉行，一班藝人都着得靚靚出場，不過總會有人失手嘅，一講到時裝車禍，大家冇可能諗唔到陳展鵬啦，今晚佢就着得正正常常嘅，不過就係條頸上面條鏈出事喇，一條銀色嘅鎖鏈，加多一條羽毛，呢個配搭係咪好熟呢？咪就係當年啲MK朋友，會加條鏈喺條褲度，陳展鵬就放咗上頸，唔知係咪單文柔幫佢諗嘅呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實陳展鵬都唔係第一次出事，之前台慶嘅時候，佢就一套白色西裝加個蓮花腰封，唔係人人咁着都好睇，至於陳展鵬好唔好睇呢？咁就要問吓單文柔喇。<br />\n<br />\n不過陳展鵬並不孤單，因為出事嘅唔只佢一個，仲有麥明詩同陳庭欣，麥明詩作為後生仔傾下計嘅主持，呢晚着得一啲都唔後生，話佢着咗媽媽條裙都有人信。陳庭欣就好似着咗件一件頭泳衣加條長裙，不過最出事係佢頸嗰塊紅色布，好似以前打功夫啲人，綁喺手上面嗰塊布，不過就佢掛上頸咁解。"},{"pid":"724f052847e9f8035fac38b0474755e69c83eb07","tid":537003,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:07:11.000Z","msg":"個條鏈好九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b05b42e57767f9d8f640bf3b1d129248f33c48","tid":537003,"uid":37997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"張圖嗰個係陳庭欣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6150fb98d1e14bf91b832c2483896c9ac74184d3","tid":537003,"uid":143768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"想睇陳庭佳"},{"pid":"a08517397866bd11abc96760c65417b1baf2aeae","tid":537003,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T01:31:30.000Z","msg":"陳庭欣圖?"},{"pid":"ef639564952ffd4aa39008909513a16befcb690c","tid":537003,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"724f052847e9f8035fac38b0474755e69c83eb07","tid":537003,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:07:11.000Z","msg":"個條鏈好九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T22:56:34.000Z","msg":"佢真係好冇fashion sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話唒都係一線小生，著得仲衰過d三四線藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}